{"tid":2118863,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日 DSE成績係點真係唔重要","createTime":"2020-07-21T18:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T01:08:55.000Z","uid":41411,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"433d75ebc814dda80a62f1f89e5608b1429a3587","tid":2118863,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"襯後生 有錢既直接去外國讀大學<br />\n無錢既咪去台灣讀大學 再係果邊做野長居<br />\n再唔係去德國 免費讀大學<br />\n香港已經無未來 唔好將個未來放係香港<br />\n<br />\n無論考得好唔好 之後讀大學定讀HD/ASSO<br />\n最最最緊要係學好英文 <br />\n<br />\n各位手足 加油！"},{"pid":"ad9ecc944c94d3cd0fbaa472bad390c6eb027f74","tid":2118863,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"有冇手足等放榜無瞓 入黎傾下計啦"},{"pid":"51dcd8c53940771e94d2c58a435abc8d304da802","tid":2118863,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:41:13.000Z","msg":"留喺香港就點都要有張好睇嘅cert <br />\n考得差嘅就認命啦"},{"pid":"de81b2cbf547c0b367e14064b33baec2e4a4a6ef","tid":2118863,"uid":81478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:47:08.000Z","msg":"Dse成績麻麻其實唔緊要<br />\n你有心機嘅 <br />\n讀u/asso/hd嘅gpa都可以洗到底<br />\n<br />\nBtw我自己覺得如果啲分唔上唔落<br />\n只係夠揀垃圾科嘅話<br />\n可以試下asso再升上去(前提係你肯比心機啦)<br />\n因為asso gpa夠高嘅話可以senior entry(asso 2年之後直入u year 3)啲本身收高分啲嘅科<br />\n到時畢業唔會同同齡人相差幾年咁<br />\n而低嘅話都可以揀返啲垃圾科<br />\n反正最差都係讀垃圾科 asso仲可以搏下"},{"pid":"17f8b3f476a5f3c333874deed4c2908237d70163","tid":2118863,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:48:11.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會考得幾分， 但搵得多過啲讀完碩士嘅同學仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713445f2110ff16a7c80e631e1d1296071c2c340","tid":2118863,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:49:45.000Z","msg":"連登仔：你係有料，唔洗入三大都搵大錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c103e93eac5a828ed8b704c1331a38cb1234eae","tid":2118863,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:52:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e33ac530a0ef29ff0d8867001d8404acbd117452","tid":2118863,"uid":105924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:54:08.000Z","msg":"如果dse成績唔太好諗住去德國讀大學既話會死得好撚慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係文科，建議人去外國讀前樓主唔該做下資料搜集先"},{"pid":"3528860f35eac7e9d8a9d7e96faa3fcb3246558b","tid":2118863,"uid":172227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T20:12:14.000Z","msg":"見到香港啲U今年搞成咁<br />\n如果冇辦法就算(基本開支，語言)，<br />\n但係有辦法，仲十五十六緊嘅，<br />\n我一律會建議走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔係喺NYC London呢啲<br />\n根本好多地方開支已經平過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你煩都係煩舊學費同住宿費<br />\n外國住宿已經平均平過香港<br />\n你住shared student accommodation 再平啲<br />\n唔會話要特別用多好多<br />\n<br />\n加上你早啲去外國，<br />\n適應吓環境都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘啲生活經驗好快用得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你香港入到神科，<br />\n拎個成績去報外國名校嘅神科一樣得<br />\n仲多啲科多啲專業俾你揀<br />\n有得去嘅Dsers真係好諗一諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c27ca556609df920d6c189113675c01e8085cb1","tid":2118863,"uid":199636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17f8b3f476a5f3c333874deed4c2908237d70163","tid":2118863,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:48:11.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會考得幾分， 但搵得多過啲讀完碩士嘅同學仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"你做狗嘅點同你比啊？"},{"pid":"245902b62b4adfd733905f8883f0947bf2ba